%b%T%b is a utility allowing IRC users to obtain
statistics on certain hostnames, domains, or servers.
To use the following commands, type: %b/msg %T <command>%b.
For more information on a specific command, type:
%b/msg %T help <command>%b.

    STATS      Gives general network statistics
    SHOWSTATS  Statistics for Chan, Nick, Memo Services
    SHOWOPERS  List currently identified irc operators
    SHOWADMINS LIST currently identified services admins

%+a%b* * * *
%+aAdministrator commands:
%+a%b%b
%+a    REFRESH    Update server lag information
%+a    CLEARSTATS Clear statistic information
%+a    GREPLOG    Grep services logs
%+a    SPLIT      Shows infomation about netsplits
%+a    HOST       List statistics for a hostname
%+a    DOMAIN     List statistics for a domain
%+a    SERVER     List statistics for a server
